title: [Gyldemar Forest, Winding Trail]
description: Animal tracks cross the trail as it twists through the trees, and some of the leaves covering the ground seem to have been recently disturbed.  Aside from a few small pieces of worked stone scattered about the exposed tree roots, there is no evidence that people ever passed this way.
